asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

description: Lola was born on a beautiful minty night in the metaverse. There was a huge attendence at her birth, and people lined up to see her beauty. Everyone wanted to touch and get hold of her. name: Flux
description: A former brigadier in the Fluf Force, this zebra furred bunny can kick like a horse. Known throughout the squadron as one to never take any prisoners, she was well respected and to be fair, slightly feared by her lesser ranking Flufs. Flux, like her eyes, was always putting the other troops on blast. She ran a tight ship, necessary given her position juxtaposed with her good looks. Too many times she had been undermined in the past, misjudged as weak, categorised as girly, elbowed aside in favour of more prototypical Fluf Force types. Despite this, Flux went on to have a glittering military career. Upon retiring earlier this year she was bestowed the red-bow badge, a symbolic reward for her years of exemplary leadership. Now searching for the right rabbit to start a fluffle with, it will take a special type to live up to her high standards.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

description: To be fair, you have to have a very high IQ to understand FLUF. The humour is extremely subtle, and without a solid grasp of theoretical physics most of the jokes will go over a typical viewer's head. There's also Fluf's nihilistic outlook, which is deftly woven into his characterisation- his personal philosophy draws heavily from Narodnaya Volya literature, for instance. The fans understand this stuff; they have the intellectual capacity to truly appreciate the depths of these jokes, to realise that they're not just funny- they say something deep about LIFE. As a consequence people who dislike Flufs truly ARE idiots- of course they wouldn't appreciate, for instance, the humour in Flufs's existential catchphrase "30 min max" which itself is a cryptic reference to Turgenev's Russian epic Fathers and Sons. I'm smirking right now just imagining one of those addlepated simpletons scratching their heads in confusion as Fluffy's business's genius wit unfolds itself on their television screens. What fools.. how I pity them.

This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

name: Devilish
description: Oh my god, I cant stop laughing. Im always playing pranks on FLUF, I dont know what gets into me. I think I have seen too many episodes of Jacka ss when I was younger. So you wanted to know about me? Well, my parents were also quite ****, big, red, shiny horns, and also used to be a bit devilish by nature. I know I have made them proud, god rest their stacks. I lost them both during the wreck. The story goes there were a number of elders in an inflatable boat and very dangerous waters. Unfortunately, their beautiful horns ended up being the downfall of them all, piercing the material and sinking boat. Gulp. Cough. Actually I cant talk about it, its still raw. Sorry. Otherwise, Im sure youve noticed my se xy little eyes. Remember, its not the size. I know they make me look super attractive, but they are slightly frustrating. I believe the scientists genetically spliced us with the Tarsier, a nocturnal monkey. . . I think that is why I find it too bright during the day and super easy to see at night. . . I guess you could call me a night owl, I mean fluf. . . I definitely stay up most of the night, the bright LED lights from the clubs reflect on my horns and really set off my good looks. Well, its getting early, I better have some rest and plan my next pranks for tonight. What are you doing later? We should hang!
